SubjectFort William First Nation Indian Reserve No. 52, Ontario ** Addition **
PrecisOrder setting apart 59.20 hectares (146.29 acres) of lands for the use and benefit of the Fort William First Nation as an ADDITION to FORT WILLIAM INDIAN RESERVE NO. 52, located at Shore Road Allowance on Pie Island, in front of Blake Township, municipality of Neebing, approximately 10 kilometres from Thunder Bay, in Ontario.
